snippet.title: 💪🏽🎖TRAINING WITH DONALD - Amber Thompson: Leaders Of Change🎖💪🏽
snippet.description:
I had the pleasure of coaching Amber Thompson through a challenging workout! Amber is the founder of Leaders of Change where she specializes in organizational development. 

The goal is to create economical and sustainable practices in communities and businesses. 

📈As a systems thinker, she helps organizations function more efficiently and being more equitable. 

Through creating this efficiency, she creates more equitable organizations by focusing on the most impacted populations (team members, community members, leaders) by creating a “bottom up” style of impact. 

⬆️”Learn bottom up to teach top down” ⬇️

This creates a more holistic environment in business and is effective with community building. 

💡Creating systems that serve well the most vulnerable people in society automatically creates a equitable environment up the ladder. 

This creates a sustainable business and community. 

📌An Example from our discussion: creating health care systems that are created to optimally serve Black residents will be even more efficient to serve more privileged members of society. 

📌Having a business flow that serves your bottom employees well creates an environment that those at the top benefit well from in addition. 

Leaders of Change works with community development organizations/civic institutions as well as corporations and small businesses that need more equitable, sustainable processes. 

Learn more & get involved with community development projects:

www.leadersofchangellc.com

And on Facebook/LinkedIn:

Info@leadersofchangellc.com

Leaders of Change LLC

Share with a friend, partner, and colleague!
